[[File:Old_cathedral_of_Kaliningrad_in_Russia.jpg|thumb]]旁邊的橋是兩條自歐拉時代保存至今的橋樑之一。]]

這七條橋之中，有兩條已經在{{link-en|第二次世界大戰對柯尼斯堡的轟炸|bombing of Königsberg in World War II|二戰時的大轟炸}}中被損毀，另外兩條則被改建成快速公路。其餘三條則原址保留，當中又有一條於1935年被重建<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amt.canberra.edu.au/koenigs.html |title=What ''Ever'' Happened to Those Bridges? |access-date=11 November 2006 |last=Taylor |first=Peter |date=December 2000 |publisher=Australian Mathematics Trust |url-status = dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319074335/http://www.amt.canberra.edu.au/koenigs.html |archive-date=19 March 2012 }}</ref>。換言之，歐拉當時的七條橋，現在只剩下五條，令奇頂點只剩下兩個，所以可以一次過走完五條橋<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.csc.ncsu.edu/faculty/stallmann/SevenBridges/ |title=The 7/5 Bridges of Koenigsberg/Kaliningrad |access-date=11 November 2006 |last=Stallmann |first=Matthias |date=July 2006}}</ref>。而從歐拉時代保存至今的就只有兩條。

